did.unittitle: Rice University News and Media Relations; Board, Administration and Faculty Photo and Research files
did.abstract: Rice University News and Media Relations has also been known in the past as News and Publications. This office creates and manages news releases on behalf of the university. The photo and biographical files in this collection were created and manitained by that office for use in such news releases.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: Rice University News and Media Relations has also been known in the past as News and Publications. This office creates and manages news releases on behalf of the university.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The photo and biographical files in this collection were created and manitained by the Rice University Office of News and Media Relations for use in the news releases generated as official Rice communications.
